https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8u9","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":23572,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/24\/medicine-cure-allah-heals\/","url_meta":{"origin":32621,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Every disease has a cure by which Allah heals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery disease has a cure. If a cure is applied to the disease, it is relieved by the permission of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2204 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19501,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/15\/ali-calamity-sin-tawbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32621,"position":1},"title":"Ali on Trials: Calamities due to sin, removed by repentance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 15, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn al-Qayyim reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cA trial is not sent down but due to a sin, and it is not lifted but with repentance.\u201d Source: al-Jawa\u0304b al-Ka\u0304fi\u0304 1\/74 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0642\u064a\u0645 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0637\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0628\u064d \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0646\u064e\u0632\u064e\u0644\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5243,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/tibb-every-disease-has-cure\/","url_meta":{"origin":32621,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah created a cure for every disease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah did not send down any disease but that he also sent its cure.\" In another narration, the Prophet said, \"One who has knowledge of it knows it, and one ignorant of it is ignorant.\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/07\/24\/seek-healing-not-haram\/","url_meta":{"origin":32621,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Seek cure for disease from what is lawful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah sent down the disease and the cure, and for every disease He made a cure. Seek treatment, but do not seek treatment by the unlawful.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3874 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17173,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/13\/believers-put-to-trial-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":32621,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Believers put to trial until all sins expiated","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believing men and women continue to be under trial in their lives, their children, and their wealth, until they meet Allah without any sin.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2399 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7286,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/29\/punish-trials-this-world\/","url_meta":{"origin":32621,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Punishment in this world as mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf Allah wills goodness for His servant, He hastens his punishment in this world. If Allah wills to harm His servant, He withholds punishment for his sins until he arrives on the Day of Resurrection.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u064